name: Levitation Control
description: Allows removing the buff Levitation (Featherfoot C2 skill) by using the skill again while the buff is active.

name: Remove Summon
description: Allows removing the buff Summoning (Sorcerer C1 skill) by using the commands: /removesummon or /rs.

name: Transpose Control
description: Allows removing the buff Transpose (Thaumaturge C1 skill) by using the skill again while the buff is active.

name: Party Invite
description: Allows inviting party members with the command /party. Example: /party Teamname
